reviewText: This video was OK for what it showed, but it is not worth the price of $ 25.00 they are charging.  Nor did they have any information on the first Sea Wolf (SSN-575)  So I suggest renting it from your local library , if its available.
Great DVD. Ordered it for my son a Navy Chief and he loves the footage. Overall Great DVD and seller. I would recommend this seller and product.
